For all your latest AVFC news, opinion, analysis and transfer gossip, click here

You can follow our Villa reporter Ashley Preece on Twitter, and his email address is Ashley.Preece@reachplc.com.
 
@AlfieAVFC1: Can we ask Jurgen Klopp if he’s a comedian.
@Designaw: If they’ll pay for the fans travel I’m up for it!
@JoshBoyle22: We’re the home team tho ? Different if Liverpool were at home @EFL
@Danielstchr: All expenses paid.
 
@GarethAVL: Yet the statement said they asked the date not to be changed.
@Tomgnargore: Klopp is shook of Villa Park. They barely got the job done against us in the league and he knows without a full strength side they will get KO'd in the cup!
@JamesyFarmer: As a Villa fan living in Qatar, I fully support this ridiculous idea

